==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Willet
<hw>Wil"let</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
large North American snipe (<spn>Symphemia semipalmata</spn>); -- called
also <altname>pill-willet</altname>, <altname>will-willet</altname>,
<altname>semipalmated tattler</altname>, or <altname>snipe</altname>,
<altname>duck snipe</altname>, and <altname>stone
curlew</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Carolina willet</b></col>, <cd>the Hudsonian
godwit.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Willful</ent>⟦br⟧
